    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and pulls well, with no known leaks or mechanical faults. The transmission shifts predictably and without hesitation. Inside, the interior is clean and well-kept, showing only minor signs of use such as slight wear on the leather upholstery and small scratches on the dashboard trim. The exterior paint retains a healthy gloss, though there are a few minor cosmetic imperfections, including small stone chips on the front bumper and a tiny scratch on the rear fender. All safety features and electronic systems are in full working order. It serves as a dependable and comfortable vehicle for daily use.",
      "price": 33000.0,
