      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior presents well, though there are minor stone chips on the front fascia and a few light scratches near the trunk handle. Mechanically, the car is sound and drives smoothly, with all major systems functioning as intended. The interior is clean and smoke-free, showing only modest wear on the upholstery and floor mats. It is a solid, reliable vehicle that offers a great balance of performance and value for its next owner.",
