    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio for surgical throttle response. The power is managed via a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and a Variable M Differential Lock, providing exceptional mechanical feedback. The chassis remains composed with a multi-link rear suspension and Electronic Damping Control (EDC) calibrated for aggressive turn-in. Recent service includes rod bearing replacement and fresh liquid-cooled oil service, ensuring the valvetrain stays within factory tolerances. While showing light patina consistent with a well-driven performance machine, the structural integrity and kinematic performance are top-tier.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
